meaningMnemonic: A <kanji>person</kanji> who has "<kanji>attain</kanji>ed" is someone who knows much. They are a <vocabulary>master</vocabulary> or <vocabulary>expert</vocabulary>, obviously.
readingMnemonic: This is a jukugo word, which usually means on'yomi readings from the kanji. If you know the readings of your kanji you'll know how to read this as well.
